title: Add padding to the bottom of the note list
message:
Add padding to the bottom of the note list

This allows the user to scroll past the last note
so that the add button doesn't block toggling the
last note in the list.

Fixes #17.

title: Implement ability to edit notes
message:
Implement ability to edit notes

Note is edited by touching it in the note list.
AddNoteActivity is used also for editing notes.

MainActivity launch mode is changed to single task
to prevent opening new instances of the activity
while there are ongoing note editing activities.

Fixes #15
